item.title: CVE-2023-32695|2024-08-02T15:25:36.835Z -- socketio -- socket.io-parser
item.description: socket.io parser is a socket.io encoder and decoder written in JavaScript complying with version 5 of socket.io-protocol. A specially crafted Socket.IO packet can trigger an uncaught exception on the Socket.IO server, thus killing the Node.js process. A patch has been released in version 4.2.3.
